DESCRIPTION: Sends a help embed in regards to permissions.
VIEW_ALL: There are six possible permission levels to have. Commands for all levels can be seen with `{{prefix}}commands`.
BLACKLISTED_VALUE_1: **Description:** Users with this role are unable to use the bot.
MEMBER_VALUE_1: **Description:** Users with this role are able to use the default commands in the bot.
MODERATOR_VALUE_1: **Description:** Users with this role are able to use moderation commands.
ADMIN_VALUE_1: **Description:** Users with this role are able to use the `$settings` command
OWNER_VALUE_1: **Description:** Users with this role are immune to all moderation commands and have access to every command. Can only be obtained if the user is the owner of the server, OR has ownership transferred to them by the current owner.
